---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Lincoln Egress Windows | Egress Window Experts in Lincoln & Southeast Nebraska"
  description="Lincoln Egress Windows installs and replaces code-compliant egress windows and window wells across Lincoln, NE and the surrounding counties. Licensed, insured, free written estimates."
  canonical="https://lincolnegresswindows.com/about/"
>
<Fragment slot="head">
<script type="application/ld+json">{"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "BreadcrumbList", "itemListElement": [{"@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://lincolnegresswindows.com/"}, {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "About", "item": "https://lincolnegresswindows.com/about/"}]}</script>
<script type="application/ld+json">{"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "FAQPage", "mainEntity": [{"@type": "Question", "name": "What areas does Lincoln Egress Windows serve?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "We serve Lincoln, NE and Southeast Nebraska, including Lancaster, Seward, Saline, and Gage counties. That covers Waverly, Hickman, Seward, Crete, Beatrice, and Ashland along with Lincoln itself."}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "Is Lincoln Egress Windows licensed and insured?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. We're licensed and insured for foundation cutting and egress window installation work, and we pull the required building permits under our license for every cut-in."}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "Do you offer free estimates?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. We give a free written estimate after seeing your foundation and site in person, since cost depends on foundation type, depth, and access. Call (509) 224-3484 or email info@lincolnegresswindows.com to set up a time."}}]}</script>
<style is:global>
  .rich p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: #555; margin: 0 0 16px; }
  .rich ul { padding-left: 20px; margin: 0 0 16px; }
  .rich li { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: #555; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .rich strong { color: #2B3A44; }
  .rich a { color: #1273A8; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; }
  .rich a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
</style>
</Fragment>

<section style="background:linear-gradient(135deg, #08344B 0%, #0E4D6E 65%, #08344B 100%);padding:72px 24px;">
  <div class="hero-grid" style="max-width:1180px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.1fr 0.9fr;gap:56px;align-items:center;">
    <div>
      <span style="display:inline-block;margin-bottom:12px;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:999px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;background:rgba(143,208,234,0.18);color:#8FD0EA;border:1px solid rgba(143,208,234,0.3);">About Us</span>
      <h1 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-weight:800;color:#fff;line-height:1.08;letter-spacing:-0.01em;font-size:clamp(30px,4.4vw,52px);margin:0 0 18px;">About Lincoln Egress Windows</h1>
      <p style="font-size:18px;line-height:1.7;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);max-width:540px;margin:0 0 28px;">We cut, install, and replace egress windows and window wells for homeowners across Lincoln and Southeast Nebraska, and we handle the permits and inspections that come with it.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px;">
        <a href="tel:+15092243484" class="btn-cream">Call Now — (509) 224-3484</a>
        <a href="/#contact" class="btn-outline-white">Get a Free Estimate</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-img" style="border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 24px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);">
      <img src="/images/about.webp" alt="About Lincoln Egress Windows" width="800" height="533" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<style>
  @media (max-width: 860px) { .hero-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; } .hero-img { max-height: 320px; } }
</style>
<section style="padding:72px 24px 40px;"><div style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;"><div class="rich"><p>Lincoln Egress Windows focuses on one job and does it right: cutting code-compliant egress windows into foundation walls and building the window wells that go with them. That focus means every crew on site has done this specific work before, on the same kind of poured concrete and block foundations found across Lincoln and Lancaster County.</p><p>A lot of basement finishing projects and home sales get held up over an egress window that was never sized or permitted correctly. We built our process around avoiding that: sizing the opening to meet IRC egress code with margin, pulling the required permits, and scheduling the inspections that make the work official rather than just finished-looking. You get a written estimate before anything is cut, and a job that passes inspection the first time.</p><p>We work on homes throughout Lincoln and out into <a href="/egress-windows-waverly/">Waverly</a>, <a href="/egress-windows-hickman/">Hickman</a>, <a href="/egress-windows-seward/">Seward</a>, <a href="/egress-windows-crete/">Crete</a>, <a href="/egress-windows-beatrice/">Beatrice</a>, and <a href="/egress-windows-ashland/">Ashland</a>, which covers Lancaster, Seward, Saline, and Gage counties. Whether it's a full <a href="/egress-window-installation-lincoln/">egress window installation</a>, an <a href="/egress-window-replacement-lincoln/">egress window replacement</a>, or just a <a href="/window-well-installation-lincoln/">window well</a> that needs rebuilding, it's the same crew and the same standard.</p><p>We're licensed and insured, and we keep a line open 24/7 for the situations that can't wait, a window well that's failing before a closing date, or a code inspection deadline coming up fast. For everything else, call us at (509) 224-3484 or email info@lincolnegresswindows.com and we'll set up a time to come look at your foundation.</p></div></div></section>
<section style="padding:0 24px 64px;"><div style="max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;">
    <span class="kicker">How We Work</span>
    <h2 class="section-heading" style="font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,32px);margin:0 0 28px;">What You Can Expect</h2>
    <div class="feat-grid" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:20px;">
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:10px;padding:26px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(14,77,110,0.05);">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 8px;">Code Compliance First</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;margin:0;">Every window we install is sized to meet IRC egress requirements with margin, not right at the minimum, so it holds up to inspection and to a future home sale.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:10px;padding:26px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(14,77,110,0.05);">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 8px;">Permits and Inspections Handled</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;margin:0;">We pull the building permit under our license and schedule the required inspections, so you're not the one tracking down the city.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:10px;padding:26px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(14,77,110,0.05);">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 8px;">Free Written Estimates</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;margin:0;">We look at the actual foundation and site before giving a number, and you get it in writing, not a guess over the phone.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:10px;padding:26px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(14,77,110,0.05);">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 8px;">Licensed, Insured, and Local</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;margin:0;">We work foundations across Lincoln and Southeast Nebraska and keep a 24/7 line open for inspections and closing deadlines that can't wait.</p>
      </div>
</div>
<style>
  @media (max-width: 860px) { .feat-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; } }
</style>
  </div></section>
<section style="padding:72px 24px;background:#EAF5FB;">
  <div style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;">
    <span class="kicker">FAQ</span>
    <h2 class="section-heading" style="font-size:clamp(24px,3.5vw,36px);margin:0 0 32px;">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;">
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:8px;padding:24px 28px;">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 10px;">What areas does Lincoln Egress Windows serve?</h3>
        <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;color:#555;margin:0;">We serve Lincoln, NE and Southeast Nebraska, including Lancaster, Seward, Saline, and Gage counties. That covers Waverly, Hickman, Seward, Crete, Beatrice, and Ashland along with Lincoln itself.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:8px;padding:24px 28px;">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 10px;">Is Lincoln Egress Windows licensed and insured?</h3>
        <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;color:#555;margin:0;">Yes. We're licensed and insured for foundation cutting and egress window installation work, and we pull the required building permits under our license for every cut-in.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:8px;padding:24px 28px;">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 10px;">Do you offer free estimates?</h3>
        <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;color:#555;margin:0;">Yes. We give a free written estimate after seeing your foundation and site in person, since cost depends on foundation type, depth, and access. Call (509) 224-3484 or email info@lincolnegresswindows.com to set up a time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="background:linear-gradient(135deg, #0E4D6E 0%, #16648C 50%, #0E4D6E 100%);padding:64px 24px;text-align:center;">
  <h2 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(26px,4vw,40px);font-weight:800;color:#fff;margin-bottom:16px;">Need Help in Lincoln & Southeast Nebraska? Call for Same-Day Service.</h2>
  <p style="font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin-bottom:28px;max-width:520px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">Free written estimates. Emergency calls answered around the clock.</p>
  <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
    <a href="tel:+15092243484" class="btn-cream">Call Now — (509) 224-3484</a>
    <a href="/#contact" class="btn-outline-white">Get Free Estimate</a>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
